### 5.3 TV Monitor — Slide 2 Layout

**Slide 1** — Bay Monitoring (active lifts, who is working)

**Slide 2** — Customer-Facing Status Board
- **Top-Left panel:** "Ready for Release" (green header) — vehicles whose service is done
- **Bottom-Left panel:** "Upcoming Vehicles" (blue header) — vehicles in queue
- **Right panel (full height):** "Carry-Over" (orange header) — vehicles staying overnight

This was built using a `flex-row` layout in HTML with `flex-col` on the left side containing two `flex-1` panels stacked vertically.

