### 5.4 Daily Intakes Table — Column Restructure

**Old structure (before):**
```
Claim Stub | Plate | Model & Category | Arrival | Departure | Parts | Evaluation | Goal (2h) | Status & Location | Remarks / Action
```

**New structure (after):**
```
Claim Stub | Plate | Model & Category | Branch | Arrival | Departure | Parts | Evaluation | [SLA Status]* | Status | Location | Remarks/Reasons | Action
