### 5.6 Location Column — Lift Occupancy Detection

When a SA opens a job's Location dropdown, the system checks **all other jobs** in memory to see which Lifts are already in use.

```
Lift 1          ← available (black text)
Lift 2 (Occupied - ABC 123)  ← disabled, red text
Lift 3          ← available
Lift 4          ← available
```

- Occupied lifts are shown in **red** and are **disabled** (cannot be selected)
- The current job's own lift is excluded from the occupancy check

