### 5.7 Analytics Dashboard (Owner Only)

The analytics section has two sub-tabs:

#### Tab 1: Live Operations Monitor
- Total Daily Intake count
- Released Today count
- Active Carry-Overs count
- In Bays (Working) count

#### Tab 2: Analytics & Reports Center

**Filters:**
- Report Scope: Daily / Weekly / Monthly
- Branch Filter: All Branches / Branch A / Branch B

**Summary Cards (with Branch A vs Branch B breakdown):**
| Card | Shows |
|---|---|
| Total Intakes | Total + Branch A count + Branch B count |
| Completed Jobs | Total + Branch A + Branch B |
| Carry Overs | Total + Branch A + Branch B |
| Avg Service Time | Overall + Branch A + Branch B |

**Charts:**
- Period Intake & Completion Trends (bar/line chart)
- Service Categories Breakdown (doughnut)
- Booking Channels Share (pie — Walk-in vs Online)

**Efficiency & Volume Insights:**
| Insight | Description |
|---|---|
| Completion Success Rate | % of completed jobs vs total |
| Complimentary Check-Ups | Count of free diagnostic jobs |
| PMS Volume | Preventive maintenance jobs |
| General Repairs (GR) | Heavy repair jobs |
| PMS Goal Success Rate | % of PMS jobs completed within 2 hours |
| PMS Success / Failure | Exact count of met vs missed 2-hour goal |
| Peak Intake Hours | Hour window with most arrivals (e.g. "9:00 AM (14 cars)") |
| Walk-in / Online Ratio | Percentage split (e.g. "72% W / 28% O") |

**Period Record Log Table:**
- Full searchable table of all jobs in the selected period
- Filters: SA Name, Service Status, Branch
- Real-time keyword search across Plate, Model, Customer, Category, SA, Status

